11:39 AM; Case called for Motion hearing.  Defendant Thomas J Washington in court with attorney Amanda Marie Nimmer.  Abbey Nickolie appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  Court notes the matter was set for hearing on Defendant's Renewed Motion to Dismiss and confirms with counsel they plan to proceed to formal hearing today.  Atty.
